beer.beer_description:
Classic international style lager brewed with 100% Irish malt and 100% Irish water. 

Style: International Lager
Malt: Irish lager malt, cara pils malt, acidulated malt
Hops: Herkules, Mittelfruh
Strength: 4.3% ABV
Bitterness: 25 IBUs

Tasting Notes
Color/appearance: pale yellow/light gold
Aroma: Very low, clean with slight biscuit
Flavour: Low in malt flavour with light and dry body. 
Aftertaste: Clean, crisp finish
